snippet.title: SpiderHeck - Official Release Date Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
SpiderHeck launches on Xbox Series X/S, Xbox One, PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, Nintendo Switch, and PC on September 22, 2022. Watch the trailer for another look at this upcoming co-op brawler game as spiders with laser weapons fight to the death.

#GameTrailers #Gaming
